[div class=p 
	"We actually managed to save 57 frames in gameplay and 239 frames by skipping the first screen of the game over 
	[a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bNGyehJGViE rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"Tomygood's previous TAS
	]a
	".
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Main strat is to avoid if possible stars or you lose 10 frames at the end of the level. No differences between jump and run only Right and run button matter.
	$LF
]div
